PN,40101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774552271
OL,3,CMayor of London "appalled" at bus
OL,4,Cdrivers working in filthy, unsafe
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FThe Mayor of London said he was
OL,8,F"appalled" by the way bus drivers are
OL,9,Ftreated, after ITV News London exposed
OL,10,Fshocking working conditions on the
OL,11,Fcapital's roads.
OL,13,FSir Sadiq Khan watched our exclusive
OL,14,Freport which revealed how drivers fell
OL,15,Fasleep at traffic lights, urinated in
OL,16,Fbottles and worked in filthy cabs.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774552271
OL,3,CMayor of London "appalled" at bus
OL,4,Cdrivers working in filthy, unsafe
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FSpeaking at the last Mayor's Question
OL,8,FTime before the elections, Sir Sadiq
OL,9,Fsaid: "We need to turn this around
OL,10,Fbecause clearly things aren't getting
OL,11,Fbetter as they should. "
OL,13,FSir Sadiq said he followed ITV News
OL,14,FLondon's report up with the Transport
OL,15,FCommissioner for London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774552271
OL,3,CMayor of London "appalled" at bus
OL,4,Cdrivers working in filthy, unsafe
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FHe continued: "So the Commission made
OL,8,Fit quite clear, both in terms of the
OL,9,Fcontacts we have with the operator,
OL,10,Fbut also the trade unions and bus
OL,11,Fdrivers, they must have direct access
OL,12,Fto let us know what's happening in
OL,13,Freality.
OL,15,F"I'll give them a recent example. I
OL,16,Fmet a bus driver at a bus garage and I
OL,17,Fwas talking to him about how great he
OL,18,Fmust find the facilities we've
OL,19,Fintroduced.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774552271
OL,3,CMayor of London "appalled" at bus
OL,4,Cdrivers working in filthy, unsafe
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,F"He told me actually, no, the reality
OL,8,Fis very different to what I've been
OL,9,Ftold about the facilities.
OL,11,F"And so we followed that up. It can't
OL,12,Fbe incumbent upon just the bus.
OL,14,F"We've got to go out there and check
OL,15,Ffor ourselves whether what the
OL,16,Foperators have told us is happening is
OL,17,Fhappening."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774552271
OL,3,CMayor of London "appalled" at bus
OL,4,Cdrivers working in filthy, unsafe
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FBut Sir Sadiq couldn't escape
OL,8,Fcriticism and was accused of failing
OL,9,Fto do enough to tackle the problem
OL,10,Fduring his ten years as mayor.
OL,12,FLeader of the Conservative Party, Neil
OL,13,FGarratt said:
OL,15,F"I mean, I've been reading this for
OL,16,Ffive years, so I'm pleased that it's
OL,17,Fnow come to your attention. I don't
OL,18,Fknow why it didn't previously.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774552271
OL,3,CMayor of London "appalled" at bus
OL,4,Cdrivers working in filthy, unsafe
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,F"One of the problems, to be blunt, is
OL,8,Fthe bus drivers just think that
OL,9,Fthey've also been banging on about
OL,10,Fthis for years, many years longer than
OL,11,FI have, and they just think that
OL,12,Fnothing will change."
OL,14,FHe told Sir Sadiq to "stop blowing
OL,15,Fyour own trumpet" as "nothing has
OL,16,Fchanged" for bus drivers over the past
OL,17,Fdecade.
OL,19,FNeil Garratt quizzed the mayor on what
OL,20,Faction will be taken to improve
OL,21,Fdrivers' conditions:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774552271
OL,3,CMayor of London "appalled" at bus
OL,4,Cdrivers working in filthy, unsafe
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,F"So in 12 months from now what will be
OL,8,Fdifferent? What will have actually
OL,9,Fchanged?"
OL,11,FSir Sadiq said that he will be
OL,12,Fintroducing regular reviews of bus
OL,13,Fschedules and drivers hours will be
OL,14,Faudited to ensure that they comply
OL,15,Fwith national regulations.
OL,17,FHe hopes that "In 12 months time we'll
OL,18,Fsee changes brought about by the bus
OL,19,Fsafety improvement including
OL,20,Fredesigning of bus cabins, improving
OL,21,Fcomfort and the cabin environment."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
